{"tid":2134803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡頌思120蚊捱1星期","createTime":"2020-08-01T04:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T17:35:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0d9b8c8e69f437e3c47e885daea2663822d1ee","tid":2134803,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=f0e3a068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估唔到Jocelyn讀中學時一星都係得120蚊使<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_03b.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=9d2290ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n難怪同學都唔知佢係有錢女！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_04b.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=ac3aa79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為細個好怕醜，所以媽咪逼Jocelyn參加戲劇班<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_05b.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=2d1fc2ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係咁發掘咗Jocelyn對舞台嘅興趣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_06b.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=75016b92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJocelyn先後參加過舞台劇同電影嘅演出，不過畀人質疑佢靠關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_07b.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=f4240eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為呢件事曾經匿埋喊過<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_10b.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=60b7a9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJocelyn笑言當時得好少零用錢，所以唔擔心男仔因為佢嘅背景而展開追求。<br />\n<br />\n早前退選港姐的「40億千金」蔡頌思（Jocelyn）入行時曾被質疑靠關係上位，幸蘇玉華的一席話令她開竅，接受自己的背景。她自言小時候家教甚嚴且零用錢不多，經常被朋友笑她是最窮有錢人。<br />\n<br />\n已故「海產大王」蔡繼有孫女蔡頌思曾一度羞於被人知道其身份，但現在面對「40億千金」的綽號已能坦然接受﹕「都幾好，令人易啲記得我，依家朋友都叫我做千金。」之前她參選港姐，可惜最終因合約問題沒有入選，原來Jocelyn因舞台劇及網大拍攝工作跟港姐合約有所牴觸，花了兩個月為參賽作準備，她坦言也大感可惜，寄望下年捲土重來。<br />\n<br />\nJocelyn小時候因性格怕醜而被母親強迫參加戲劇班，意外發掘她對舞台的興趣，亦令她變得開朗及主動，大學畢業後更放膽追夢，做全職演員。Jocelyn星運不俗，先後在舞台劇及電影跟蘇玉華與袁詠儀合作，但因背景而被質疑靠關係去獲取角色，令她情緒崩潰：「有日蘇玉華見我偷偷喊就安慰我，佢話導演揀得你一定有佢嘅原因，你就係你，唔可以滿足到每一個人，呢番說話啟發我好多，以前我會收收埋埋唔想畀人知我背景，但依家學懂接受。」<br />\n<br />\n出身名門的Jocelyn自小家教嚴格，求學時家中禁睇電視、禁玩遊戲機、禁跟朋友出街、禁零食與有味飲料，而且零用錢不多，Jocelyn不得不省吃儉用﹕「我一星期包埋交通費只有120蚊零用錢，出入都係搭巴士、地鐵，朋友話我係最窮嘅有錢人。好多人都睇唔出我咁有錢，以為大家家境差不多。我全家人都好慳，咁都幾好，訓練到我拍戲就算冇人服待、食飯冇得揀，我都冇問題。」至於拍拖，雖然母親自小向Jocelyn灌輸要出來工作才可談戀愛的觀念，不過，Jocelyn考畢A level後就初戀，問到會否擔心男方因其背景而追求她？她說：「中學大家都好純粹，唔會睇背景，而且我細個零用錢咁少，冇人覺得我係有錢。」Jocelyn稱現時單身，擇偶條件首要愛錫她、有上進心及笑容好看的男生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001.html&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=303864d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6d51f6637f2a6ca1b468ca14f8b9a35faa1374b3","tid":2134803,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:10:09.000Z","msg":"120蚊？<br />\n40年前？"},{"pid":"db1ccc80787a45955d2999cb11d5ca2ad54681cb","tid":2134803,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"邊撚個黎？個樣咁老扮後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cc72b6f0d76ae670e92052da827aaef2d1aba1","tid":2134803,"uid":9281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"no one cares"},{"pid":"8a69ed80d559c4cae529a014396ad23b9736738f","tid":2134803,"uid":22839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"我出$360過夜比佢捱多三個星期"},{"pid":"6a1cf22f5780161cafa1c94241fa877326a91cd8","tid":2134803,"uid":54452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"有條件發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1986ca1b5280d697ded36284db8eedcb2ac37750","tid":2134803,"uid":290414,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb0d9b8c8e69f437e3c47e885daea2663822d1ee","tid":2134803,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200801/photo/bkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200801000343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200801000016593-0801_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200801000343&h=f0e3a068&s={SIZE}\"